What is the horizontal shift from f to g?

Find all values of x for which \sin (x-\dfrac{\pi}{3})=1, for -\pi \le x \le \pi.

Find all values of x for which \sin (x-\dfrac{\pi}{3})=0, for -\pi \le x \le \pi.

